  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is conducted in Africa. The aim of this study is to assess the safety and efficacy
      of Levemir® treatment for insulin naive patients with type 2 diabetes under normal clinical
      practice conditions in Algeria.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
